<i>NUMERO VEINTE CUATRO,</i>

00:28.300 --> 00:30.900
KEN GRIFFEY JR.

00:30.900 --> 00:33.000
[IMITATES CROWD CHEERING]

00:33.000 --> 00:35.700
[ALARM CLOCK SOUNDS]

00:35.700 --> 00:38.767
ERIC, YOU WERE
DOING IT AGAIN.

00:38.767 --> 00:39.967
WHAT, THE JENNY McCARTHY
DREAM

00:39.967 --> 00:41.900
OR THE SPANISH BASEBALL
ANNOUNCING?

