WHY DON'T YOU
GO OUT ON A DATE?

09:00.800 --> 09:02.300
YOU USED TO DATE
ALL THE TIME.

09:02.300 --> 09:04.300
I KNOW,
BUT ALL THE GIRLS
I USED TO DATE

09:04.300 --> 09:05.467
HAVE GONE OFF
TO COLLEGE.

09:05.467 --> 09:07.667
OH, I'M SURE THERE'S
PLENTY OF NICE GIRLS

09:07.667 --> 09:08.667
RIGHT HERE IN TOWN.

09:08.667 --> 09:11.300
TOWNIES? YOU WANT ME
TO DATE A TOWNIE?

09:11.300 --> 09:12.800
OH, THAT IS GREAT, MOM.

09:12.800 --> 09:13.900
I CAN SEE THEM
RIGHT NOW

09:13.900 --> 09:16.233
SITTING ON THEIR COUCH
IN THEIR RATTY BATHROBE,

09:16.233 --> 09:19.600
WATCHING DAYTIME TV,
EATING BONBONS.

09:20.700 --> 09:23.767
THESE ARE
COCOA PUFFS.

09:24.934 --> 09:27.367
AND I'M A DETECTIVE.

09:31.967 --> 09:35.967
I DON'T KNOW, MAN.
SHE'S BEEN IN THERE
AN AWFUL LONG TIME.

09:35.967 --> 09:38.300
WHAT ARE YOU
GETTING SO CRAZY ABOUT?

09:38.300 --> 09:39.600
SHE'S JUST
GETTING A HAIRCUT.

09:39.600 --> 09:41.300
NO, COR. WE'VE KNOWN
TOPANGA ALL HER LIFE, OK?

09:41.300 --> 09:42.900
SHE DOESN'T WEAR MAKE-UP.

09:42.900 --> 09:45.767
SHE'S NEVER BEEN
TO A BEAUTY PARLOR.
SHE'S COMPLETELY NATURAL.

09:45.767 --> 09:47.300
SO WHAT'S THE BIG DEAL?

09:47.300 --> 09:51.300
THE BIG DEAL IS
SHE WAS BEAUTIFUL BEFORE
WITHOUT ANYBODY'S HELP.

09:51.300 --> 09:52.500
NOW SHE'S GOT
PROFESSIONAL HELP.

09:52.500 --> 09:53.867
SHE'S GONNA BE
MEGA-BEAUTIFUL.

09:53.867 --> 09:56.400
WE'RE NOT EVEN
GONNA BE ABLE TO
LOOK AT HER DIRECTLY

09:56.400 --> 09:57.500
WITHOUT BURNING
OUR RETINAS.

09:57.500 --> 10:00.367
SHAWN, COME ON.
THIS IS NOT
BEVERLY HILLS.

10:00.367 --> 10:02.400
I MEAN, IT'S
A NEIGHBORHOOD
BEAUTY SALON

10:02.400 --> 10:03.900
NEXT TO
OLD LADY SCHNEIDER'S
DOUGHNUT SHOP.

10:03.900 --> 10:06.734
I MEAN,
THEY DON'T EXACTLY
DO MIRACLES HERE.

10:10.033 --> 10:11.600
OLD LADY SCHNEIDER.

10:11.600 --> 10:13.867
IT'S A MIRACLE!

10:15.233 --> 10:16.934
OH, NO.

10:16.934 --> 10:18.400
SHAWN, TOPANGA
IS GONNA COME OUT

10:18.400 --> 10:20.467
LOOKING 10 TIMES BETTER
THAN SHE DID
WHEN SHE WENT IN.

10:20.467 --> 10:22.834
OK, THE FIRST THING
SHE'S GONNA DO
IS DUMP YOU,

10:22.834 --> 10:23.900
THEN STARTING
HANGING OUT

10:23.900 --> 10:25.934
WITH OTHER UNBELIEVABLY
GOOD-LOOKING PEOPLE.

10:25.934 --> 10:27.100
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

10:27.100 --> 10:28.300
IT'S WHAT WE DO.

10:28.300 --> 10:29.667
UH-HUH. UH-HUH.

10:29.667 --> 10:33.500
WELL, I THINK
THAT'S INTERESTING,
BUT, OH, SO WRONG.

10:33.500 --> 10:34.600
AND WHY IS THAT?

10:34.600 --> 10:36.734
BECAUSE IF ANYBODY
KNOWS HAIR, IT'S ME.

10:36.734 --> 10:37.934
WHEN I
GET A HAIRCUT,

10:37.934 --> 10:40.834
IT LOOKS TERRIBLE
FOR, LIKE,
THE FIRST SIX WEEKS.

10:40.834 --> 10:42.033
THEN
ALL OF A SUDDEN,

10:42.033 --> 10:44.767
IT LOOKS TERRIFIC
FOR, LIKE, A DAY.

10:44.767 --> 10:46.233
THEN IT'S TIME
FOR ANOTHER HAIRCUT.

10:46.233 --> 10:48.100
IT'S WHAT
I LIKE TO CALL

10:48.100 --> 10:49.700
THE HAIRCUT CYCLE
OF SHAME.

10:49.700 --> 10:52.467
OK, AND THAT'S
WHAT YOU THINK'S
GONNA HAPPEN TO TOPANGA?

10:52.467 --> 10:54.867
YES, I DO BECAUSE
THE UNIVERSE KNOWS

10:54.867 --> 10:57.400
THAT TOPANGA AND I
ARE SUPPOSED TO BE
TOGETHER,

10:57.400 --> 10:59.000
SO THE UNIVERSE
HAS SEEN FIT

10:59.000 --> 11:00.300
TO PUT TOPANGA
IN THAT CHAIR

11:00.300 --> 11:01.300
AND MAKE HER HIDEOUS

11:01.300 --> 11:03.200
SO WE CAN GET THROUGH
OUR TEENAGE YEARS

11:03.200 --> 11:06.233
AWKWARD HAND
IN AWKWARD HAND.

11:06.233 --> 11:07.400
YOU KNOW SHE'S COMING
OUT GREAT-LOOKING,
DON'T YOU?

11:07.400 --> 11:09.300
YES!

11:22.200 --> 11:23.400
THIS UNIVERSE BLOWS!

