11:38.200 --> 11:39.200
SHAWN!

11:39.200 --> 11:41.667
SHUT UP, MAN!
I'M GOING FOR IT!

11:41.667 --> 11:43.200
THANKS. THANKS.
I'M BACK.

11:43.200 --> 11:44.200
GOOD.

11:44.200 --> 11:46.233
ALL RIGHT, TOPANGA,
I WANT--

11:46.233 --> 11:48.367
I WANT THE NAME OF THE GUY
WHO DID THIS TO YOU.

11:48.367 --> 11:49.500
YOU DON'T LIKE IT?

11:49.500 --> 11:50.667
NO, NO, IT'S NOT
THAT I DON'T LIKE IT,

11:50.667 --> 11:52.133
IT'S JUST THAT
I'M IN LOVE WITH THIS GIRL

11:52.133 --> 11:54.467
WHO WAS NEVER INTERESTED
IN WHAT SHE LOOKED LIKE BEFORE,

11:54.467 --> 11:55.900
AND NOW I SEE MAKE-UP
ON YOUR FACE

11:55.900 --> 11:57.700
AND POLISH ON
YOUR NAILS AND TOES AND--

11:57.700 --> 11:59.200
STOP LOOKING AT HER TOES.

11:59.200 --> 12:01.000
