SPARKLE.

12:01.000 --> 12:03.500
I WANT THE NAME OF THE GUY
WHO DID THIS TO YOU.

12:03.500 --> 12:05.367
MY STYLIST'S NAME
IS MR. CELLINI.

12:05.367 --> 12:07.800
CORY, IT'S JUST A HAIRCUT.
IT'S JUST SOME MAKE-UP.

12:07.800 --> 12:10.200
IT'S NOT GOING
TO CHANGE ME.

12:10.200 --> 12:11.300
GOTTA GO.

12:11.300 --> 12:12.500
WELL, WHERE
ARE YOU GOING?

12:12.500 --> 12:13.734
THIS OUTFIT
WITH THIS HAIR?

12:13.734 --> 12:16.967
HELLO, BYE-BYE.
I AM SO AT THE MALL.

12:18.400 --> 12:20.400
YOU KNOW, SHAWN,
THIS JUST ISN'T
LIKE TOPANGA.

12:20.400 --> 12:22.100
OBVIOUSLY, SHE'S
UNDER THE INFLUENCE

12:22.100 --> 12:23.600
OF THIS SO-CALLED
MR. CELLINI.

12:23.600 --> 12:24.967
YEAH. I SAY
WE GO BACK THERE.

12:24.967 --> 12:27.200
YOU ARE MY FRIEND,
AREN'T YOU?

12:27.200 --> 12:28.200
OF COURSE I AM.

12:28.200 --> 12:29.834
AND THAT LITTLE THING
WITH TOPANGA?

12:29.834 --> 12:34.200
WELL, I THINK
THE 3 OF US CAN BE
VERY HAPPY TOGETHER.

12:35.667 --> 12:39.600
ALL RIGHT, WHICH ONE
OF YOU GUYS WORKED
ON TOPANGA LAWRENCE?

12:39.600 --> 12:43.100
AH, THAT WOULD BE ME--
BOSCO CELLINI.

12:43.100 --> 12:45.567
ALL RIGHT, BOSCO,
I WANT TO KNOW
WHERE YOU COME OFF

12:45.567 --> 12:47.100
TAKING A NATURAL BEAUTY
LIKE TOPANGA

12:47.100 --> 12:50.734
AND PAINTING HER FACE
AND NAILS AND MESSING
WITH HER BEAUTIFUL HAIR?

12:50.734 --> 12:51.734
"MESSING"?

12:51.734 --> 12:55.000
HEY, FRIEND TO
THE LITTLE WHINING BOY,

12:55.000 --> 12:56.600
DID HE SAY "MESSING"?

12:56.600 --> 12:57.600
YEAH. THAT'S
WHAT I HEARD.

12:57.600 --> 13:00.500
WELL, FOR
YOUR<i>INFORMAZIONE,</i>

13:00.500 --> 13:02.734
IT IS VERY RARE
THAT ON A TUESDAY--

13:02.734 --> 13:03.867
OUR SLOW DAY--

13:03.867 --> 13:07.467
THAT VENUS DE MILO HERSELF
WOULD SIT IN MY CHAIR

13:07.467 --> 13:11.100
AND SAY TO ME,
"MAKE WITH ME
WHAT YOU WISH."

13:11.100 --> 13:15.400
I AM A EUROPEAN MAN
SECURE ENOUGH IN
MY OWN MASCULINITY

13:15.400 --> 13:17.934
TO ADMIT TO YOU
I WEPT.

13:17.934 --> 13:20.834
I CRIED LIKE
A LITTLE BABY CRIES.

13:20.834 --> 13:22.000
ALL RIGHT, BOSCO,
FIRST OF ALL,

13:22.000 --> 13:23.600
WE'RE IN THE MIDDLE
OF PHILADELPHIA
HERE,

13:23.600 --> 13:25.400
SO LET'S JUST DROP
THIS PHONY ACCENT.

13:25.400 --> 13:26.500
<i>SCUSI?</i>

13:26.500 --> 13:27.767
TALK IN ENGLISH!

13:29.200 --> 13:30.400
[BROOKLYN ACCENT]
ALL RIGHT, HERE'S
HOW IT WENT DOWN.

13:30.400 --> 13:34.100
CHICKY COMES IN,
PLOPS DOWN A HALF
A C-NOTE, RIGHT?

13:34.100 --> 13:35.934
I DO A LITTLE
SNIPPETY-SNIP,

13:35.934 --> 13:39.734
BADDA-BOOM, BADDA-BING,
YOUR GIRLFRIEND'S A LOOKER.

13:39.734 --> 13:43.867
YOU'RE RIGHT.
I MEAN, SHE IS BEAUTIFUL.

13:43.867 --> 13:45.100
OK, LET'S GO, BUDDY.

13:45.100 --> 13:46.467
