LEFT FOR YOU HERE.

13:46.467 --> 13:48.000
YOU DID A VERY NICE JOB.

13:48.000 --> 13:50.667
HEY, DON'T MENTION IT.

13:57.767 --> 13:59.367
SO I'M KIND OF AT
THE CROSSROADS OF MY LIFE

13:59.367 --> 14:02.100
BECAUSE I DIDN'T
GET INTO COLLEGE LIKE
THE REST OF MY FRIENDS.

14:02.100 --> 14:03.500
OH, YOU DIDN'T?

14:03.500 --> 14:06.767
NO. LOOKS LIKE
I'M KIND OF STUCK HERE
IN TOWN FOR A WHILE.

14:06.767 --> 14:09.400
IT'S NOT SO BAD.
REALLY.

14:09.400 --> 14:10.400
