14:31.567 --> 14:35.600
YEAH. I MEAN,
I HAVE A 2-YEAR-OLD
TO TAKE CARE OF.

14:35.600 --> 14:37.767
HE'S A BIG HANDFUL,

14:37.767 --> 14:40.600
