YOUR MOM AND DAD
HELPING YOU?

14:51.033 --> 14:53.900
WELL, YOU KNOW,
JUST...FINANCIALLY.

14:56.133 --> 14:58.367
THAT'S NICE.

14:58.367 --> 15:00.467
YOU'RE VERY LUCKY,
ERIC.

15:00.467 --> 15:02.033
YEAH, THANKS.

