15:31.700 --> 15:34.367
WITH HIS WONDERFUL
INNER SPIRIT.

15:34.367 --> 15:35.500
YEAH, YOU KNOW WHAT?

15:35.500 --> 15:37.300
I COME FROM
A GREAT-LOOKING FAMILY,

15:37.300 --> 15:38.967
