MY AWKWARD TEENAGE PHASE,

15:38.967 --> 15:42.500
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN
I CAN'T WIN THE HEARTS
OF HIGH SCHOOL SOCIETY

15:42.500 --> 15:44.000
WITH MY WONDERFUL
INNER SPIRIT.

15:44.000 --> 15:46.900
NOW, SEE, WHAT'S
REALLY INTERESTING
ABOUT JOHN MERRICK

15:46.900 --> 15:49.834
IS THAT HE CAME FROM
A WONDERFUL-LOOKING FAMILY,

15:49.834 --> 15:51.400
YET WAS SO HIDEOUS HIMSELF,

15:51.400 --> 15:53.600
HE WAS FORCED TO WEAR
A BURLAP SACK OVER HIS HEAD

15:53.600 --> 15:55.800
AND PERFORM
AS A SIDESHOW FREAK

15:55.800 --> 16:00.600
