CELLINI THE ARTIST.

16:50.300 --> 16:52.400
I WANT YOU TO HELP ME
LIKE YOU HELPED TOPANGA.

16:52.400 --> 16:53.700
FORGET IT!
I DON'T TAKE WALK-INS.

16:53.700 --> 16:55.600
